{"id": "aos034", "name": "Audio_Trans_03_702_12_26", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call Starts]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Hello, hello? Noah!?</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Helena, it's me.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Aroma? Are you okay!?</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Yeah... I'm alright.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Why are you just calling me now? I saw the news that 03 was also attacked by drones, but your phone wasn't working...</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I'm sorry. So much has happened recently, I had to wait until now to call.\nI've been pretty good, and even got my memories back.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Really?</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Yeah... Anyway, I'm with NEKO and them on a train to 08. I'll head back in a few days.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Okay, that's wonderful... really...</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Sis, are you okay?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>I... I'm great, nothing's going on...</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "You sound strange, I can tell...\n... Is it something with Noah...?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>......\nHa... You've really grown up.</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Helena?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>... After you left, I told him about you leaving and tried to convince him that it was for the best. But he just couldn't accept it. We got into a huge fight... We didn't talk for a few days. Just did our own things in the house without even looking at each other.</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Then... about 2 weeks ago, I woke up and... he was gone</i>.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Gone...?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>So when you called, I thought it was Noah... He was so angry...</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Ah, what am I doing. Why am I talking about this? You don't need to worry. After he thinks it over, he'll come home.</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I'm sorry.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Aigh, you don't need to apologize! Oh, you said you got your memory back? Then hurry up and come... come...</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Sis?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Other... wise... I-I... I'm gonna...</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Call Ends]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Tuner-San]"], "content": "<i>Your battery has no power, please charge immediately.</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Eh!?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>What's wrong PAFF?</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Tuner-san cut off while I was talking to my sister. Ran out of electricity...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>I see... The core in my chair and ROBO can produce electricity, but this device is a bit old. Our current equipment is unable to charge it.\nI'm sorry, there's nothing I can do.</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "No, it's okay... it's just...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Just what?</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "If possible, I'd like to go home first... But we're on such a tight schedule, don't we need to make a move right away?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... It shouldn't be an issue.\nI'll let Mr. Neumann know.</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Really?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>You need to make sure your family isn't worried, right? We can take that risk. Let's go.</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Yeah... okay.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>もしもし……もしもし？ Noah！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃん、私。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Aroma？あなた大丈夫なの！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……私は大丈夫だよ。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>なんで今まで連絡くれなかったの？\n03がドローンに攻撃されたってニュースで見て……あなたの電話もつながらないし……</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ごめんね。\n色々あって、連絡するのが今になっちゃったの。\n私は元気だよ。それに、記憶も取り戻した。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>本当に？</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……それで私ね、NEKOたちと08に向かってるの。\n数日でそっちに着くと思う。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>そう。よかった……本当に……</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃんは……大丈夫？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>私は……私は大丈夫よ。何も……</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "でも声の様子がおかしいよ。\n隠さないで？私には分かるんだから……\n……Noahさんと……何かあった？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>………\nはは…… Aromaも大きくなったのね……</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃん？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>……あなたが出発した後、あの人に私があなたを連れて行ったことを話したの。\n説得……してみようと思って。\nでも、あの人は受け入れてくれなかった……ケンカになって……数日間口もきかずに、家の中でもお互い存在しないものとして過ごしてた。</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>それから……2週間くらい前かな……目を覚ましたら、あの人いなくなってたのよ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "いなくなった……？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>だから、あなたが電話をかけてきた時、Noahだと思ったの……きっと今度こそ本当に頭にきたんだわ……</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>あはは……私ったらなんでこんな話……\nあなたは心配しないでいいのよ。\nNoahだって、心の整理ができたら帰ってくるはずだから。</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ごめんなさい……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>もう！あなたが謝る必要はないでしょ！\nそうだ、記憶が戻ったんでしょう？なら早く帰っ……て……</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "お姉ちゃん？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>じゃな……と……お姉……ん……</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話終了]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[チューナー君]"], "content": "<i>電池切レ！充電充電！</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "そんな！？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>どうかした？PAFFさん。</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "まだお姉ちゃんと話してるところだったのに、チューナー君の充電が……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "そう……私の車いすとROBOはコアで電力を生み出すことができるけど、このデバイスは少し古いから、ここにある機材では充電できそうにない。\n役に立てなくてごめんなさい。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "ううん、いいの……ただ……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ただ？</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "もし可能なら、いったん家に帰ることってできる……？\nでも、この状況じゃすぐに行動に移したほうがいいよね？やっぱり……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……いいえ。そうしましょう。\n私がNeumannさんに伝えておく。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "本当に？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>あなたのことを大切に思ってる人に心配かけたくないんでしょう？\nそれくらいなら大丈夫。行ってきて。</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "うん……わかった。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>喂、喂？ Noah！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊，是我。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Aroma？妳還好嗎！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……我沒事。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>怎麼現在才聯絡？我看到 03 也被無人機攻擊的新聞，妳的電話也打不通……</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "對不起，前陣子發生太多事情，所以現在才打給妳。\n我過得很好，也找回記憶了。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>真的嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……總之，我和 NEKO 她們現在已經在往 08 的列車上，過幾天就會回去了。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>那就好，太好了……真的……</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊，妳還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>我……我很好啊，什麼事都沒有……</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "妳的語氣怪怪的，我聽得出來……\n……和 Noah 有關係……嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>……。\n哈…… Aroma 真的長大了呢……</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>……妳離開之後，我和他說了帶走妳的事，並試著說服他。但他怎麼也無法接受，和我大吵一架……我們好幾天不說話，在家裡也各做各的事，看都不看對方。</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>後來……大概兩個禮拜多前吧，我醒來後發現……他不見了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不見了……？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>所以妳打來時，我還以為是 Noah……這次他真的是太生氣了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>啊，真是的，我怎麼在說這些？妳不用擔心，Noah 想通之後就會回來的。</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "對不起……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>哎唷，妳才不需要道歉呢！對了，妳說妳找到記憶了？那就快……回回……</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>不……然……我我……會……</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話結束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>電力耗盡，請立即充電。</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦！？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>怎麼了嗎，PAFF 小姐？</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "剛剛和姊姊講到一半，喇叭君就沒電了……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>這樣啊……我的輪椅和 ROBO 雖然能從核心產生電能，但這台裝置有點舊了，我無法透過現有的設備給它充電。\n抱歉，幫不上忙。</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不，沒關係的……只是……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>只是？</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "可以的話，我想先回家一趟……但是情況那麼緊急，我們是不是趕快展開行動比較好？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……無妨，就這麼辦。\n我去和 Neumann 先生說一聲。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "真的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>是為了不讓重視妳的人擔心吧？這樣的風險我們可以承擔。去吧。</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……好的。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 시작]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>여보세요, 여보세요?  Noah! ? </i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니, 나야.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Aroma? 무사한 거니! ? </i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "응......난 괜찮아.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>왜 지금에서야 연락한 거야! 03에서 드론 테러 사건 터졌다고 뉴스 나왔는데도 전화 한 통도 없고...</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "미안해. \n앞전에 좀 여러가지 일들이 생겨서, 지금에서야 언니한테 연락하게 됐네.\n난 잘 지내고 있어. 그리고... 기억들도 되찾았어.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>정말이니!?</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "응......아무튼 나랑 NEKO씨 일행이랑 같이 08로 가는 열차에 타고 있어. 며칠 뒤면 아마 도착할 거야.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>정말... 정말 다행이야... 정말로...</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니는... 괜찮아?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>나는......괜찮아. 아무 문제 없이 잘 지내고 있어...</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "말투가 뭔가 다른데... 내가 모를 줄 알아?\n....Noah씨랑 관련된 일 때문에 그러지?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>......\n하하...... Aroma도 이제 어른이구나...</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>......네가 떠나고 나서 그이한테 내가 널 데리고 갔다고 얘길 했거든... 설득해보려고 하는데 계속 받아들이지 못하고 결국은 엄청 크게 싸웠거든... 벌써 며칠이나 서로 아무 얘기도 안하고 집안에 있어도 서로 본 척도 안하고 각자 할일만 하고 있는 상황이야.</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>그리고......2주전이었을 거야... 그때서야... 그 사람이 사라졌다는 걸 알게 됐어.</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "사라졌다고......? \n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>그래서 네 전화를 받았을 때, Noah가 건 전화인줄 알고...... 이번엔 정말 제대로 화가 난 건지...</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>에휴, 정말! 어째서 이런 얘기를 하고 있는 거지? 걱정마~ Noah도 화가 좀 가라앉으면 바로 돌아올 거니까.</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "미안해......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>어허! 니가 왜 사과를 하고 그래! 아 참, 기억을 되찾았다고 했지? 그럼 빨리.... 돌....</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "언니?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>그렇......으면......나......는......</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[통화 종료]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[튜너군]"], "content": "<i>배터리 부족!\n충전 요망! 충전 요망!</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "뭐라고!?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>무슨 일입니까, PAFF 씨? </i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "방금 언니랑 얼마 얘기 하지도 않았는데, 튜너군 배터리가...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "그렇군요......제 휠체어와 ROBO의 코어에는 전력 공급 기능이 있긴 한데, 이 디바이스는 너무 구형입니다. 현재 가진 수단으로는 충전할 방법이 없습니다.\n도움이 못돼서 죄송합니다.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "아니, 괜찮아요... 다만...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>다만?</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "만악 가능하다면, 집에 한번 다녀오고 싶은데.... 하지만 이런 긴박한 상황에서는... 역시 곧바로 작전에 참여하는 게 맞는 거겠죠?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......아니요. 그럼 그렇게 하시죠.\nNeumann 씨에게는 제가 잘 말해둘 테니.</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "정말 그래도 돼요!?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>당신을 소중하게 생각하는 사람들에게 걱정을 끼치고 싶지 않아서 그런 거잖아요. 그 정도는 괜찮으니까, 다녀오세요.</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "네... 알겠어요.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話開始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>喂、喂？ Noah！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊，是我。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Aroma？妳還好嗎！？</i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……我沒事。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>怎麼現在才聯絡？我看到 03 也被無人機攻擊的新聞，妳的電話也打不通……</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "對不起，前陣子發生太多事情，所以現在才打給妳。\n我過得很好，也找回記憶了。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>真的嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……總之，我和 NEKO 她們現在已經在往 08 的列車上，過幾天就會回去了。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>那就好，太好了……真的……</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊，妳還好嗎？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>我……我很好啊，什麼事都沒有……</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "妳的語氣怪怪的，我聽得出來……\n……和 Noah 有關係……嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>……。\n哈…… Aroma 真的長大了呢……</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>……妳離開之後，我和他說了帶走妳的事，並試著說服他。但他怎麼也無法接受，和我大吵一架……我們好幾天不說話，在家裡也各做各的事，看都不看對方。</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>後來……大概兩個禮拜多前吧，我醒來後發現……他不見了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不見了……？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>所以妳打來時，我還以為是 Noah……這次他真的是太生氣了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>啊，真是的，我怎麼在說這些？妳不用擔心，Noah 想通之後就會回來的。</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "對不起……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>哎唷，妳才不需要道歉呢！對了，妳說妳找到記憶了？那就快……回回……</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>不……然……我我……會……</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通話結束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>電力耗盡，請立即充電。</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦！？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>怎麼了嗎，PAFF 小姐？</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "剛剛和姊姊講到一半，喇叭君就沒電了……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>這樣啊……我的輪椅和 ROBO 雖然能從核心產生電能，但這台裝置有點舊了，我無法透過現有的設備給它充電。\n抱歉，幫不上忙。</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不，沒關係的……只是……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>只是？</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "可以的話，我想先回家一趟……但是情況那麼緊急，我們是不是趕快展開行動比較好？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……無妨，就這麼辦。\n我去和 Neumann 先生說一聲。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "真的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>是為了不讓重視妳的人擔心吧？這樣的風險我們可以承擔。去吧。</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……好的。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通话开始]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>喂、喂？ Noah！ ？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊，是我。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>Aroma？妳还好吗！ ？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……我没事。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>怎么现在才联络？我看到 03 也被无人机攻击的新闻，妳的电话也打不通……</i>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "对不起，前阵子发生太多事情，所以现在才打给妳。\n我过得很好，也找回记忆了。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>真的吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……总之，我和 NEKO 她们现在已经在往 08 的列车上，过几天就会回去了。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>那就好，太好了……真的……</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊，妳还好吗？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>我……我很好啊，什么事都没有……</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "妳的语气怪怪的，我听得出来……\n……和 Noah 有关系……吗？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>……。\n哈…… Aroma 真的长大了呢……</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>……妳离开之后，我和他说了带走妳的事，并试着说服他。但他怎么也无法接受，和我大吵一架……我们好几天不说话，在家里也各做各的事，看都不看对方。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>后来……大概两个礼拜多前吧，我醒来后发现……他不见了。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不见了……？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>所以妳打来时，我还以为是 Noah……这次他真的是太生气了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>啊，真是的，我怎么在说这些？妳不用担心，Noah 想通之后就会回来的。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "对不起……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>哎唷，妳才不需要道歉呢！对了，妳說妳找到记忆了？那就快……回回……</i>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "姊姊？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Helena]"], "content": "<i>不……然……我我……会……</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[通话结束]</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[喇叭君]"], "content": "<i>电力耗尽，请立即充电。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "咦！ ？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>怎么了吗，PAFF 小姐？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "刚刚和姊姊讲到一半，喇叭君就没电了……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>这样啊……我的轮椅和 ROBO 虽然能从核心产生电能，但这台装置有点旧了，我无法透过现有的设备给它充电。\n抱歉，帮不上忙。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "不，没关系的……只是……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>只是？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "可以的话，我想先回家一趟……但是情况那么紧急，我们是不是赶快展开行动比较好？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……无妨，就这么办。\n我去和 Neumann 先生说一声。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "真的吗？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>是为了不让重视妳的人担心吧？这样的风险我们可以承担。去吧。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "嗯……好的。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}